summary:
A multi-skilled and result-oriented marketing communication and business development professional with over 10 years of experience, including the engineering and international relations sectors. A proven track-record of marketing activities on B2B market and in business events organization at European level. Native Russian speaker with excellent knowledge of French, English and Italian.

Core competencies:
- Defining and creating comprehensive marketing strategies
- Creating and driving successful marketing campaigns
- Managing marketing projects (marketing materials, publications) 
- Event management 
- Business consultancy
- B2B marketing
- Internal marketing
- Analysis and effective product management
- Teaching

Skills:
- Excellent communication skills
- Ability to build and maintain strategic relationships at a senior level, including significant channel partner management
- Exceptional consulting and decision-making skills
- Ability to learn fast and to present information in a comprehensive way
- Analytical thinking
